July 11, 2026 (code review fixes — second pass)

- Fixed TOCTOU race in admin.service resolveNoShow: assertBookingNotAlreadyStruck was called
  inside the $transaction callback using the non-transactional prisma client; concurrent admin
  requests could both pass the check and insert duplicate strikes. Moved assertion before tx.
- Fixed 404→403 regression in UsersAssertions.assertUserIsActive: missing users now throw
  ForbiddenException (matching old assert.util.ts behaviour), preventing account-existence
  leakage via HTTP status code difference
- Fixed misleading ForbiddenException in ReviewsService.create: null customerProfile was
  coerced to '' and passed to assertCustomerOwnsBooking; added explicit NotFoundException guard
- Fixed hardcoded literal 3 in bookings.service handleWorkerCancellationPenalty: now imports
  and uses STRIKE_SUSPENSION_THRESHOLD so threshold changes apply to both strike paths
- Fixed strikePayload spread order in admin.service strikeWorker: changed
  { issuedBy: user.sub, ...dto } to { ...dto, issuedBy: user.sub } so admin sub always wins
- Fixed assertWorkerIsUnverified double DB fetch in admin.assertions: now composes with
  assertWorkerProfileExists instead of issuing its own findUnique
- Standardised assertBookingExists error message in admin.assertions to 'Booking not found.'
  matching BookingsAssertions; added NotFoundException test for null-profile path in reviews spec
- Test count: 160 → 161

